---
/**
 * Blog Section — "The Engineering Log"
 * Teaser cards for published and upcoming posts
 */
---

<section class="blog-section" id="blog">
  <div class="section">
    <p class="section-label">// The Engineering Log</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Experiments, Not Marketing</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      We document our experiments with the same rigor we write our code.
      No hype. Just data.
    </p>

    <div class="blog-grid">
      <!-- Published -->
      <article class="blog-card blog-featured">
        <div class="blog-tag">Latest</div>
        <h3 class="blog-title">What If Identity Search Didn't Need Deep Learning?</h3>
        <p class="blog-excerpt">
          A four-step graph walk, with zero hidden layers, solved an adversarial
          doppelgänger trap that stumps deep learning. Energy cost: one LED blink.
        </p>
        <div class="blog-meta">
          <span>February 2026</span>
          <span>·</span>
          <span>8 min read</span>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="blog-link">Read the experiment →</a>
      </article>

      <!-- Coming Soon -->
      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-tag blog-tag-upcoming">Coming Soon</div>
        <h3 class="blog-title">The 1-Watt Challenge: Chess Without GPUs</h3>
        <p class="blog-excerpt">
          Can structured navigation beat a grandmaster-level engine
          using less energy than a lightbulb?
        </p>
        <div class="blog-meta">
          <span>March 2026</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-tag blog-tag-upcoming">Coming Soon</div>
        <h3 class="blog-title">Financial Regime Detection Without Retraining</h3>
        <p class="blog-excerpt">
          How topological memory lets a trading agent recognize market shifts
          it has never seen — without forgetting what it already knows.
        </p>
        <div class="blog-meta">
          <span>Q2 2026</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-tag blog-tag-upcoming">Coming Soon</div>
        <h3 class="blog-title">Medical Triage: Routing Without Neural Networks</h3>
        <p class="blog-excerpt">
          A stateful navigation agent that routes emergency patients
          using structured memory instead of deep classifiers.
        </p>
        <div class="blog-meta">
          <span>Q2 2026</span>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .blog-section { background: var(--void); }
  .blog-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .blog-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .blog-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent-dim); }
  .blog-featured {
    grid-column: span 2;
    border-color: rgba(0,255,136,0.2);
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,255,136,0.03), transparent),
      var(--surface);
  }
  .blog-tag {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--accent-glow);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .blog-tag-upcoming {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    background: var(--surface-2);
  }
  .blog-title {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .blog-excerpt {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .blog-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .blog-link {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .blog-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .blog-featured { grid-column: span 1; }
  }
</style>
